  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Icon_Tinkering.png\" class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tinkering.png/85px-Icon_Tinkering.png?e55c2d\" width=\"85\" height=\"104\" class=\"thumbimage\"></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Icon_Tinkering.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Tab Icon.</div></div></div>\n<div><b>“</b><span>My work awaits!</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wagstaff\" title=\"Wagstaff\">Wagstaff</a></p>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Tinkering Tab</b> is an exclusive <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">crafting</a> tab that is only available to <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wagstaff\" title=\"Wagstaff\">Wagstaff</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Craftable_Items_and_Structures\">Craftable Items and Structures</span></h2>\n<p>The following items and structures can be crafted in the Tinkering Tab:\n</p>\n<div><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spectoggles\" title=\"Spectoggles\"><img alt=\"Spectoggles\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Spectoggles.png?2a9913\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spectoggles\" title=\"Spectoggles\">Spectoggles</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Infroggles\" title=\"Infroggles\"><img alt=\"Infroggles\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Infroggles.png?558606\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Infroggles\" title=\"Infroggles\">Infroggles</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Visor\" title=\"Visor\"><img alt=\"Visor\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Visor.png?78b338\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Visor\" title=\"Visor\">Visor</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fryfocals\" title=\"Fryfocals\"><img alt=\"Fryfocals\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fryfocals.png?b24e91\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fryfocals\" title=\"Fryfocals\">Fryfocals</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Telebrella\" title=\"Telebrella\"><img alt=\"Telebrella\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Telebrella.png?6f32e0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Telebrella\" title=\"Telebrella\">Telebrella</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Telipad\" title=\"Telipad\"><img alt=\"Telipad\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Telipad.png?179be2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Telipad\" title=\"Telipad\">Telipad</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Thumper\" title=\"Thumper\"><img alt=\"Thumper\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Thumper.png?6661fe\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Thumper\" title=\"Thumper\">Thumper</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Electrical_Doodad\" title=\"Electrical Doodad\"><img alt=\"Electrical Doodad\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Electrical_Doodad.png?d7bfec\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Electrical_Doodad\" title=\"Electrical Doodad\">Electrical Doodad</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
